# Power BI Dashboard Extension

As an extension of the MLM Lead Conversion Analysis project, I created an interactive Power BI dashboard to present the analysis in a more visual and user-friendly way. The dashboard was built to help users quickly understand lead conversion trends and identify key insights.


The dashboard included visualizations showing:

 - Lead conversions across different social media platforms (Facebook, Instagram, TikTok)
 - Gender distribution of leads
 - Performance of different ad types (Video, Image, Carousel)
 - The relationship between interest levels and follow-up frequency
 - The relationship between interest levels and follow-up frequency
 - Product category filters (Beauty, Finance, Health) for interactive analysis

This extension helped turn the data analysis into a simple dashboard that makes insights easier to understand and supports better business decision-making.
 

